<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gurú Nutricional IA</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">

    <div id="user-profile-modal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-75 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-50">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 w-full max-w-md">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Crea tu Perfil Nutricional</h2>
            <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-6">Completa tus datos para personalizar tu plan.</p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div><label for="alias" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Nombre o Alias</label><input type="text" id="alias" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"></div>
                <div><label for="age" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Edad</label><input type="number" id="age" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"></div>
                <div><label for="height" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Altura (cm)</label><input type="number" id="height" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"></div>
                <div><label for="weight" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Peso Actual (kg)</label><input type="number" id="weight" step="0.1" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"></div>
                <div><label for="gender" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Sexo</label><select id="gender" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"><option value="M">Masculino</option><option value="F">Femenino</option></select></div>
                <div><label for="activityKey" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Nivel de Actividad</label><select id="activityKey" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"><option value="sedentary">Sedentario</option><option value="light">Ligero</option><option value="moderate">Moderado</option><option value="active">Activo</option></select></div>
                <button id="save-profile-button" class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 flex justify-center items-center">
                    <span class="btn-text">Guardar y Crear Plan</span>
                    <div class="btn-loader hidden"></div>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="plan-setup-modal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-75 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-50">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 w-full max-w-lg">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Crea tu Plan de Pérdida de Peso</h2>
            <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-6">Elige cómo quieres alcanzar tu objetivo.</p>
            <div class="mb-4 border-b border-gray-200"><nav class="flex -mb-px" id="plan-tabs"><button data-plan-type="byPace" class="plan-tab-button border-b-2 border-blue-500 text-blue-600 py-4 px-1 text-center font-medium w-1/2">Por Ritmo</button><button data-plan-type="byKg" class="plan-tab-button border-transparent text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300 py-4 px-1 text-center font-medium w-1/2">Por Meta Específica</button></nav></div>
            <div id="plan-content" class="space-y-4">
                <div id="plan-byPace" class="plan-type-content space-y-4">
                    <div><label for="pace" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Ritmo de pérdida</label><select id="pace" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"><option value="0.25">Suave (~0.25 kg/sem)</option><option value="0.5" selected>Estándar (~0.5 kg/sem)</option><option value="0.75">Agresivo (~0.75 kg/sem)</option></select></div>
                    <div><label for="pace-days" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Duración (días)</label><input type="number" id="pace-days" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm" value="30"></div>
                </div>
                <div id="plan-byKg" class="plan-type-content hidden space-y-4">
                    <div><label for="kg-goal" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Kg a perder</label><input type="number" id="kg-goal" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm" value="3"></div>
                    <div><label for="kg-days" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">¿En cuántos días?</label><input type="number" id="kg-days" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm" value="45"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="plan-preview" class="mt-6 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hidden">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-center mb-2">Resumen de tu Plan</h3>
                <div id="plan-summary-text" class="text-center text-gray-800"></div>
                <div id="plan-warnings" class="mt-3 text-sm text-yellow-800 bg-yellow-100 p-3 rounded-md"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex mt-6 gap-4"><button id="calculate-plan-button" class="w-1/2 bg-gray-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-700">Previsualizar Plan</button><button id="save-plan-button" class="w-1/2 bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 disabled:bg-gray-400" disabled>Guardar e Iniciar</button></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="edit-profile-modal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-75 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-50">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 w-full max-w-md">
            <div id="edit-profile-loader" class="text-center hidden"><div class="loader mx-auto"></div><p class="mt-4">Cargando perfil...</p></div>
            <div id="edit-profile-form">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Editar mi Perfil</h2>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div><label for="edit-alias" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Nombre o Alias</label><input type="text" id="edit-alias" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"></div>
                    <div><label for="edit-age" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Edad</label><input type="number" id="edit-age" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"></div>
                    <div><label for="edit-height" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Altura (cm)</label><input type="number" id="edit-height" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"></div>
                    <div><label for="edit-weight" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Peso Actual (kg)</label><input type="number" id="edit-weight" step="0.1" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"></div>
                    <div><label for="edit-gender" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Sexo</label><select id="edit-gender" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"><option value="M">Masculino</option><option value="F">Femenino</option></select></div>
                    <div><label for="edit-activityKey" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Nivel de Actividad</label><select id="edit-activityKey" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm"><option value="sedentary">Sedentario</option><option value="light">Ligero</option><option value="moderate">Moderado</option><option value="active">Activo</option></select></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex mt-6 gap-4">
                    <button id="cancel-edit-button" class="w-1/2 bg-gray-300 text-gray-800 font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-400">Cancelar</button>
                    <button id="save-changes-button" class="w-1/2 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 flex justify-center items-center">
                        <span class="btn-text">Guardar Cambios</span>
                        <div class="btn-loader hidden"></div>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="custom-alert-modal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-75 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-50">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 w-full max-w-md text-center">
            <h2 id="custom-alert-title" class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Título del Mensaje</h2>
            <p id="custom-alert-message" class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Este es el cuerpo del mensaje.</p>
            <div id="custom-alert-buttons" class="flex justify-center gap-4">
                <button id="custom-alert-cancel-button" class="w-1/2 bg-gray-300 text-gray-800 font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-400">Cancelar</button>
                <button id="custom-alert-confirm-button" class="w-1/2 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Aceptar</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-6 sm:p-8 w-full max-w-2xl relative">
        
        <div id="settings-menu-container" class="hidden absolute top-4 right-4">
            <button id="settings-button" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-800">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
            </button>
            <div id="settings-dropdown" class="hidden absolute right-0 mt-2 w-48 bg-white rounded-md shadow-lg py-1 z-10">
                <a href="#" id="edit-profile-link" class="block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100">Editar Perfil</a>
                <a href="#" id="delete-data-link" class="block px-4 py-2 text-sm text-red-600 hover:bg-red-50">Eliminar Todos los Datos</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <div id="datetime-display" class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2"></div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Gurú Nutricional IA 🥗</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">Sube una foto y obtén un análisis nutricional completo.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="nutrition-tracker" class="hidden text-center bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-800">Mi Progreso Diario</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-5 items-center mt-2 gap-2">
                <div><div id="calorie-goal" class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600"></div><div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Kcal Objetivo</div></div>
                <div class="hidden sm:block text-3xl font-light text-gray-400">-</div>
                <div><div id="calories-consumed" class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600"></div><div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Kcal Consumidas</div></div>
                <div class="hidden sm:block text-3xl font-light text-gray-400">=</div>
                <div><div id="calories-remaining" class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600"></div><div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Kcal Restantes</div></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="file-input-container bg-gray-50">
                <div id="upload-prompt" class="text-center text-gray-500">
                    <svg class="mx-auto h-12 w-12 text-gray-400" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 48 48"><path d="M28 8H12a4 4 0 00-4 4v20m32-12v8m0 0v8a4 4 0 01-4 4H12a4 4 0 01-4-4v-4m32-4l-3.172-3.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0L28 28M8 32l9.172-9.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L28 28m0 0l4 4m4-24h8m-4-4v8" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>
                    <p class="mt-1">Haz clic para subir una foto</p>
                </div>
                <img id="image-preview" class="hidden" alt="Vista previa de la imagen">
                <input id="file-input" type="file" accept="image/*">
            </div>
            <button id="analyze-button" class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 disabled:bg-gray-400">Analizar Plato</button>
        </div>

        <div id="results-container" class="mt-8 hidden">
            <div id="loader" class="flex justify-center items-center py-8 hidden"><div class="loader"></div><p class="ml-4 text-gray-600">Analizando...</p></div>
            <div id="result-content" class="hidden">
                <h2 id="dish-name" class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-2"></h2>
                <div id="portion-analysis-text" class="text-center text-sm text-gray-700 bg-yellow-100 p-3 rounded-md mb-6 border"></div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-center">Ingredientes y Calorías</h3>
                    <ul id="cart-list" class="space-y-2"></ul>
                </div>
                <button id="add-calories-button" class="hidden mt-6 w-full bg-green-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-600 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6" /></svg>
                    Añadir a mi día
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="error-message" class="hidden text-center text-red-600 bg-red-100 p-4 rounded-lg"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center mt-8">
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Versión 1.5 - Final</p>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
